  The star looked sensational as she showed off her ageless figure in a bright red bikini. The former musical theatre actress, who could be seen paddling on a secluded beach, kept her blonde hair swept back off her face and accessorised with a pair of dark sunglasses. “Goodbye sunshine,” she captioned the snap with a red love heart emoji. “Back on @thisisheart tomorrow morning from 6:30am,” the presenter confirmed to her Heart Radio fans.  